Metadata.Title: Employee Mismanagement
Metadata.Description: Greetings, 47.We have been tasked by a disgruntled Kronstadt HR Staffer to remove 5 employees. These targets had quite the drunken night, trashing the center at the previous race, as well as replacing the drink in the winner's cup with urine and writing "*BLEEP* Kronstadt" in graffiti. They appear to believe that they have gotten away with this scott free, however they are mistaken. The staffer would like to minimise any further risk of disruption, so stealth will be necessary.  Good Luck, 47.
